474
00:31:52,439 --> 00:31:54,350
Hello? Laurie

475
00:31:59,079 --> 00:32:00,915
Michael.

476
00:32:00,915 --> 00:32:03,696
Thank you so much for stopping
by on your way to the airport.

477
00:32:03,696 --> 00:32:05,891
I wanted to be able to say thank you in person.

478
00:32:05,891 --> 00:32:08,014
Wha.. ah, you don't need to thank me.

479
00:32:08,014 --> 00:32:09,526
You know, you paid me to do a job,

480
00:32:09,526 --> 00:32:12,598
I'm just happy that I was
