481
00:32:12,598 --> 00:32:15,511
Oh, Michael.

482
00:32:15,511 --> 00:32:16,891
Come in.

483
00:32:19,631 --> 00:32:21,396
Michael.

484
00:32:21,396 --> 00:32:24,530
